---
title: Pork Sausages & Cheesy American Potatoes with Apple & Carrot Salad
description: Pork and apple are old mates from way back – and the sweet and savoury combo works just as well when the apple is part of a crisp salad. Continue the theme with cheese and potato, another delicious duo that makes this an all-star dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-sausages-cheesy-american-potatoes-f859478d.jpg
